  "keyFeatures": [
    "Importer of Record (IOR) — legal Thai entity for importing without establishing a local company",
    "Thai FDA registration for cosmetics, food supplements, and medical devices",
    "Trademark registration via Thai DIP and Madrid Protocol",
    "International logistics (air, sea FCL/LCL, courier) from Korea to Thailand",
    "Bonded warehouse and general fulfillment center in Bangkok",
    "Shopee Thailand seller account management and product listing optimization",
    "Shopee campaign management (Flash Sale, Mega Campaigns, Brand Day)",
    "Digital marketing: TikTok, Facebook, Instagram, LINE OA, KOL/influencer campaigns",
